Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:28.05,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.10,0:01:58.14,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part A}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.65,0:11:15.70,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:25.71,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Part B}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.33,0:22:30.37,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.42,0:24:00.46,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Epilogue}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.44,0:24:19.48,Default,chptr,0,0,0,,{Preview}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.34,0:00:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,My, your journey's proven to be quite a long one.{wow, no "welcome to the velvet room"}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.68,0:00:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to resolve your ordeal in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.27,0:00:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There isn't much time left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.69,0:00:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to reach out to the truth?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.53,0:00:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You could call this the moment of truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.66,0:02:02.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll take you to a place...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.96,0:02:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,where you can be at peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.97,0:02:23.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I did the best I could to look into it,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's nothing that would indicate the sender's identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.27,0:02:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.65,0:02:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.19,0:02:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Since he personally left it in your mailbox,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.70,0:02:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it's highly likely that the culprit is closer to us than we think.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.03,0:02:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We should probably look for clues around that area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.08,0:02:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're like a regular Sherlock Holmes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.79,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, you're like a totally different person when you talk about the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.54,0:02:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Y-You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.71,0:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Who cares?! That's not what's important!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.22,0:02:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,A dangerous criminal found out where he lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.55,0:03:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows what'll happen if we don't do something?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.72,0:03:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.93,0:03:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.35,0:03:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Worried?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.15,0:03:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're absolutely right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.61,0:03:11.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful, Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.40,0:03:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Give us a call if anything happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.98,0:03:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.16,0:03:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I may be looking at this differently than everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.75,0:03:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.55,0:03:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsumi was right earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.93,0:03:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Considering the situation, I should be concerned for your safety first and foremost.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.14,0:03:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But I...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.02,0:03:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I probably have no right to be your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.27,0:03:44.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Not when I hold solving the case as my top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.32,0:03:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll see you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.08,0:04:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Big Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.75,0:04:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Now for our next story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}There's been much conjecture on the origin of the fog,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.51,0:04:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}and some are concerned about its effects on the human body.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.43,0:04:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you lost your appetite?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.85,0:04:25.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In response, Mr. Kozai of the Environmental Concern Society
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.48,0:04:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-uh. I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}visited a local elementary school to investigate the effects of the fog.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.86,0:04:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he came to my school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.49,0:04:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.82,0:04:35.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Today, I spoke with a young student who spoke her own mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}free from the influence of those around her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}It was an attitude and example that we as adults can learn from.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.45,0:04:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.67,0:04:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're burning up!{ufufufufu}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.17,0:04:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because it was cold today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.17,0:04:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I hate the cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.55,0:04:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be spring soon enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.34,0:04:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it'll warm right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.89,0:05:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,But aren't you leaving in the spring?{;_;}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.31,0:05:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to make snowmen with you when it snows!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Let's make a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.66,0:05:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.29,0:05:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.37,0:05:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's play a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, let's play a whole lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.44,0:05:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:06:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's impossible to tell who it was based off that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.28,0:06:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Be sure to watch the Midnight Channel tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.30,0:06:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.58,0:06:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Something up?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.33,0:06:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.34,0:06:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.42,0:06:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like your fever's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's still cold out,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.13,0:06:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so you should go to bed early tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.84,0:06:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Aww! But I wanna watch TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.60,0:06:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.68,0:06:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You need to hurry and get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. So you have a space heater!{kotatsu lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.94,0:06:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy said we could use it if we got cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.19,0:06:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.74,0:06:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.74,0:06:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.87,0:06:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.66,0:06:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go buy a new one later.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.66,0:06:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.96,0:06:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Can we get it at Junes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.60,0:06:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.63,0:06:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We can get Yosuke to cut us a deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.54,0:06:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay, I love Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.21,0:06:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Daddy's back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome ho—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,This was in the mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.85,0:07:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.10,0:07:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.41,0:07:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear what this is all about.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.16,0:07:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you don't want to discuss this here, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.54,0:07:47.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We're heading out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy! Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.13,0:07:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay. We're just going out to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.05,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be back soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.31,0:08:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu, I think of you as a member of the family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,That's precisely why I should've done this sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.86,0:08:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.03,0:08:18.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to tell me everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,From what you're involved in to how you got involved. Everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.54,0:08:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I also think of you as family.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.13,0:08:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.13,0:08:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,About everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.55,0:08:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We've...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.39,0:08:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,been involved in the serial murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.64,0:08:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,We rescue the people who get kidnapped...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.90,0:08:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,by going inside the TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.57,0:08:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Inside the TV?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.61,0:08:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,There are enemies called "Shadows," which we fight using Personas—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.49,0:09:03.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It hasn't been long enough for you to trust me like your old man,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.16,0:09:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,but I hoped you'd open up to me a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.90,0:09:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle, please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.55,0:09:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Send this to the lab.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.21,0:09:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.72,0:09:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.34,0:09:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay here for the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.77,0:09:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.35,0:09:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima's just worried about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.73,0:09:34.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was probably just tough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.11,0:09:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be just outside this room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.70,0:09:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Call if you need anything, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.33,0:09:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, why do I have to pitch in with stock duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.33,0:09:54.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}The 8 o'clock clearance sale has begun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.34,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm not working hard enough! There's no getting around it!{lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.13,0:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I really shouldn't have gotten this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.80,0:10:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotten what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.64,0:10:06.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang onto it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.35,0:10:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your own cell. We'd get worried if we couldn't reach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.48,0:10:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Thank you, Yosuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.40,0:10:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You use it by... Scrap that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just show you how I use mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.65,0:10:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}At Junes, every day is Customer Appreciation Day!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.20,0:10:22.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll give Yu a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.20,0:10:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Every day's great at your Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.96,0:10:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try his home phone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.96,0:10:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.92,0:10:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Nanako? Is Yu around?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.26,0:10:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Nana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.63,0:10:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}If it's Nana, give the phone to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.26,0:10:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not home. He got a weird letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.26,0:10:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Daddy got mad when he saw it and took him to the police station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The police station?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.14,0:10:51.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Gimme the phone! Gimme the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.56,0:10:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's at the door. I gotta go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.02,0:10:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nana, it's your bear-y good friend Teddie!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.85,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, sorry to bother you. See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.15,0:10:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Lemme talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.90,0:10:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You hung up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.44,0:11:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,A letter? It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.04,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.76,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,How could it be her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.30,0:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,She hasn't been on TV!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.05,0:11:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, she {\i1}was{\i0} on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.05,0:11:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako wasn't seen, but she was heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.18,0:11:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.64,0:11:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the politician who visited a local school
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.02,0:11:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,and made the news several times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.19,0:11:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,In those interviews,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.32,0:11:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,he always quoted a particular student he spoke with.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.94,0:11:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah, I remember watching that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.41,0:11:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The child became well-known,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.03,0:11:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,while remaining anonymous.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl was Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.16,0:11:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.37,0:12:01.25,Default,,0,0,0,,A reporter who took interest in this
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,released her photo and interview using her real name in today's evening paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.92,0:12:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,But even before that, this is a small rural town.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.25,0:12:12.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Her identity must've been circulating for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.88,0:12:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've realized it much sooner!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was so hung up on the idea of people who were "shown" on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.89,0:12:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are we gonna do? Nanako's home alone right now, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.69,0:12:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm on my way there as we speak to check on her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.94,0:12:32.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please let me out, Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.41,0:12:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.33,0:12:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako... Nanako's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.37,0:12:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.88,0:12:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't open that door!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.42,0:12:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Fuck off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.38,0:12:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Rawr!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.42,0:12:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to talk to Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.92,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Hey, stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.59,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.88,0:12:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yosuke?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you think you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako's missing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.81,0:13:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.02,0:13:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Shirogane.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.57,0:13:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirogane, you there? What the hell's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.99,0:13:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The front door was open, and there was no one inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.37,0:13:27.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid that Nanako's been kidnapped by the serial killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.88,0:13:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, surely you must've known.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,The case isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.93,0:13:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The number you have dialed is unavailable right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.93,0:13:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'd like, you may leave a mess—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.31,0:13:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?! Why Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.69,0:13:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.44,0:13:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.36,0:13:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go look for my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.28,0:14:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But do you even have any ideas or leads on who took her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:01.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a checkpoint by the highway.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That won't help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.83,0:14:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.12,0:14:06.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.91,0:14:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.33,0:14:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.75,0:14:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I can't let you go! Yu, be reasonable!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.09,0:14:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut your fuckin' mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.01,0:14:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Open the door!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nana's in a bear-y dangerous situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.43,0:14:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta go save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nana's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.09,0:14:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What'll you do if something happens to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.51,0:14:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You gonna take responsibility if something happens to Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.06,0:14:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to call back-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.14,0:14:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.31,0:14:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,They're multiplying!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.10,0:14:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.35,0:14:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.65,0:14:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, did they lock you in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.48,0:14:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, please release him and the others!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.45,0:14:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you know I can't do—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Move aside, Naoto!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.87,0:14:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I know how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,but if you don't tell me what's going on,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.70,0:14:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,there's really nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, so you agree to release them once we explain the situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.88,0:14:58.13,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, that's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.38,0:14:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Naoto, we don't have time for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.96,0:15:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.93,0:15:05.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's all take a moment to stop and sort out the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.26,0:15:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps this will help Adachi understand as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.97,0:15:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.35,0:15:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.43,0:15:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,if we run out blindly, we'll have no idea where to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.06,0:15:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no doubt in my mind that this is a kidnapping by the same culprit who was behind the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.15,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, consider that the front door at Nanako's house was open.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.28,0:15:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I examined it and found no trace that entry had been forced.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Nanako opened the door herself?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit didn't sneak in. He boldly came up to the front door and rung the doorbell.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.00,0:15:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Like how it was for all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.71,0:15:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... "For all of us"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But the circumstances are different for her compared to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Remember what Nanako said when we were at the hot springs?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(275,275)}"I always do what my dad tells me, like not opening the door for strangers!"
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.97,0:15:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,So is the killer someone Nanako knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.48,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Huh? What? How'd you figure that out?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.23,0:15:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like we're closing in on who it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But we need more info.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.90,0:16:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Then let us change our perspective slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.40,0:16:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,His quick work is what stood out to me when he caught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.74,0:16:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You said he threw you in immediately after being kidnapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.49,0:16:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I would go as far as to say that it took place in front of their houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.70,0:16:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Meaning he had a TV out front.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The culprit is taking a TV with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.79,0:16:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Precisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.09,0:16:26.76,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, it's highly likely that he drives to the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.76,0:16:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,And it would take a car large enough to hold a fairly big TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.72,0:16:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A large car...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.68,0:16:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no unusual vehicles have been sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.68,0:16:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect someone to notice since most of the victims vanished during the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.73,0:16:43.27,Default,,0,0,0,,So it's someone Nanako knows who has a car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.73,0:16:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's a car that can't be seen?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.78,0:16:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's one you wouldn't notice even if you saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.62,0:17:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A delivery truck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.88,0:17:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.50,0:17:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,A delivery came! It was a delivery truck!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.71,0:17:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No one looks twice at a delivery truck, no matter where it's parked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.68,0:17:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If it were a local company, it'd be the same deliveryman every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.47,0:17:17.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So that explains it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.06,0:17:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi, is there anyone who fits this profile?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.81,0:17:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I don't really know.{adachi, the misterx of policemen}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.98,0:17:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you're not too far off base.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima put this stuff together to reinvestigate the first case,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.91,0:17:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and one of the suspects for Ms. Yamano's murder was a deliveryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.24,0:17:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I think he was a city council secretary before becoming a deliveryman.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.67,Default,,0,0,0,,A secretary? That's Namatame Taro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.96,0:17:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The guy who had the affair with Ms. Yamano?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.17,0:17:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Adachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.01,0:17:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's been a break in the case, I'd better hurry to the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.74,0:18:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll just have to hope nothing happens here while I'm gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.57,0:18:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.87,0:18:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang in there, Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.29,0:18:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On a road by the highway! If this isn't urgent—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.88,0:18:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The perp! I know who the culprit is!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just as you suspected!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the deliveryman!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.72,0:18:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Namatame!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.30,0:18:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Namatame Taro!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's leave Namatame's car to Dojima and Adachi for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.94,0:18:51.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Take us to Junes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.94,0:18:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.45,0:19:05.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's headed for the highway via the shopping district's main street!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.16,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not letting you get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.26,0:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.91,0:19:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.13,0:19:55.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Dojima, hang in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.00,0:19:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.92,0:19:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Where's Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.72,0:20:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? We need an ambulance, quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.51,0:20:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.89,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.98,0:20:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And Namatame?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.11,0:20:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't! We have to preserve the crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.36,0:20:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.28,0:20:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hanamura, pay him!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.28,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude! I swear, I'm not your sugar daddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.87,0:20:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The door's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.87,0:20:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.96,0:20:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I found this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.13,0:20:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There really is a TV in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.13,0:20:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Narukami?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.55,0:20:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.97,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go rescue Nanako!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.55,0:20:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What if you end up somewhere dangerous?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.56,0:20:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to try!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.56,0:20:53.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{Senpai}Stop it! If we fail, who's going to save Nanako?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:20:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,This diary...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.07,0:21:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}They're doing their own thing again...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.53,0:21:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,It probably belonged to Namatame.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:04.53,Default,,0,0,0,,"I discovered the existence of a new world."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.53,0:21:07.37,Default,,0,0,0,,"Thus, I must save people."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.37,0:21:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,"Save"?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.79,0:21:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The hell's he mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.67,0:21:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a list of the victims' home addresses!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.92,0:21:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamano Mayumi, Konishi Saki,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Amagi Yukiko, Tatsumi Kanji, Kujikawa Rise...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.22,0:21:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even the victims who survived and were never released to the public are written here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.97,0:21:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I note that Mr. Morooka's address is absent from the list.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... Then that settles it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.52,0:21:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The last date is today's.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.69,0:21:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,"I can't believe such a small child appeared on it."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.86,0:21:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,"I must save this child, no matter what."
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that... about Nanako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.88,0:22:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.42,0:22:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Uncle!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.68,0:22:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.10,0:22:13.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nanako...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.48,0:22:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,She's my reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,You can save her, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.07,0:22:22.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Please save her for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.24,0:22:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I {\i1}will{\i0} save her!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.12,0:24:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be okay now.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.92,0:24:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I shall...{raep tiem}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.43,0:24:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just killing people!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We just have to believe in them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.60,0:24:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, get out of the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.06,0:24:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a {\i1}savior!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.23,0:24:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Big Bro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.40,0:24:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it. Stop it!
